      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you need to do a &amp;lsquo;diff&amp;rsquo; on 2 folders and one of them is remote then you can accomplish that as follows:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ diff &amp;lt;(ssh username@192.168.1.60 ls -R /home/username/dir1) &amp;lt;(ls -R /home/username/dir2) &#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description>
